---
title: Harissa and Honey-Glazed Tofu with Almond Couscous and Garlic Sauce
description: Smoky, fragrant and subtly spicy harissa meets sweet and sticky honey to create bold, caramelized flavour in this succulent tofu dish. A creamy garlic-lemon sauce brings balance and dimension to both the tofu and couscous.
